{"tid":420103,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"samsung note 8 集中討論區！","createTime":"2017-10-01T06:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T02:53:30.000Z","uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75e0a99a38b8b8c742d23840529aa3944c40135c","tid":420103,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"大家收到貨未，電量 各方面如何?<br />\n<br />\nDisplayMate三星Note8擁有智能手機史上最強螢幕<br />\n=================================<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/142052_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F142052_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=0b0c367b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/142056_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F142056_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=e2792f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專門評測各類裝置顯示器表現的DisplayMate指出，Note 8所使用的6.3吋顯示器，亮度峰值超過1200 nits，即使在戶外也能呈現較佳的螢幕可讀性，加上呈現更精確與飽和的色彩，為智能型手機有史以來最佳的顯示器。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 8<br />\n<br />\n專門評測各種裝置之顯示器的DisplayMate Technologies本周指出，三星於上周發表的Galaxy Note 8是該實驗室有史以來所測試的智能型手機顯示器中最創新、效能也最好的，獲得了最高等級的A+成績。<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 8採用6.3吋的顯示器，比前一代的5.7吋大了14%，由於它幾無邊框，因此手機尺寸仍與前一代相當。此外，DisplayMate發現Note 8不只在OLED顯示器硬件上有所改善，也有許多新的顯示器功能，且亮度比Galaxy S8增加了22%，峰值顯示亮度超過1200 nits，創下智能型手機顯示器的新紀錄，不論在室內或戶外的光線環境下都有更佳的螢幕可讀性。<br />\n<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n<br />\nGalaxy Note 8顯示器的其他特色還包括其解像度高達2960x1440，支持4K電視所使用的DCI-P3寬色域，其原生色飽和度達到DCI-P3的112%及sRGB / Rec.709色域的141%，在高亮度環境下的顯示器顏色也更漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n整體而言，DisplayMate認為Note 8的顯示器提供非常傑出的影像質量，有精確的色彩，也有寬色域的鮮艷彩色模式，具備高亮度與低反射率，很好的觀看角度，堪稱是頂級的智能型手機顯示器。"},{"pid":"2755dfccab1c112e354790523294eb3002c77483","tid":420103,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:32:14.000Z","msg":"想買金色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0151a30db302d786cad6537d0cbf65e2b5d0fc59","tid":420103,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"好過iPhone 脹機啦下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e86c78762032988f62a739d970542a822a8cbe","tid":420103,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想買金色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍色好正啵"},{"pid":"8cd8db53879015a85e93dde5fd9e9608c16ecd9e","tid":420103,"uid":140852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想買金色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藍色好正啵</blockquote><br />\n都係鐘意白色或者金色啲<br />\n但兩隻都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇人講話出IPHONEX果陣<br />\n就會出金色打<br />\n諗落*有啲可能*<br />\n唯有等下睇下有無機會好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8f32de1b73431e873c4b7b02662ed07c12357f","tid":420103,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"外型係幾靚，再睇下啲內置apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"72395e3f5fdc0dd71482c179865958df5b6394dc","tid":420103,"uid":142653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce69e32b877ddd1d0f0d8854e5b11dd2a3638299","tid":420103,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"有冇8+既轉過note8?<br />\n我想知兩部機電量比較"},{"pid":"aa438614b49353a11c6c13754fb31766f899c89d","tid":420103,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇8+既轉過note8?<br />\n我想知兩部機電量比較</blockquote><br />\n暫時唔知係咪ios11問題，note8同樣用法電量你預長3